{"data":[{"date":"15:48 23/08","title":"PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/1/22/psg-nang-gia-hoi-mua-rakitic-len-90-trieu-euro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Rakitic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh PSG duy nh\u1ea5t Verratti l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, nh\u01b0ng Rabiot hay Thiago Motta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u01b0 v\u1eady s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 90 tri\u1ec7u euro, PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 90 tri\u1ec7u euro, PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/22/Chi-90-trieu-euro,-PSG-rat-muon-mua-Ivan-Rakitic--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Rakitic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Thomas Tuchel r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao. Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Ph\u00e1p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh PSG quan t\u00e2m Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Barca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 Rakitic l\u00ean t\u1edbi 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 PSG kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Rakitic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-bat-ngo-ra-yeu-sach-voi-barca-180-195091.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rakitic \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi</span>, anh cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n kho\u1ea3n th\u00f9 lao 130.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Rakitic l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Barca l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/6/PSG-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-Barca-len-90-trieu-euro-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Rakitic l\u00ean 90 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. 90 tri\u1ec7u euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 30 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady PSG mu\u1ed1n Barca nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia, PSG s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00f2i 110 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Milinkovic-Savic, song PSG \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 80 ho\u1eb7c 90 tri\u1ec7u euro s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. PSG c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2695","checkdouble":"195161"},{"date":"15:44 23/08","title":"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/dinhtrongngay238dl_jpau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n sau khi d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng chi\u1ec1u qua, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bu\u1ed9c HLV Park Hang Seo ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng?\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>1. Bi\u1ebfn V\u0103n H\u1eadu l\u00e0m trung v\u1ec7 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eafc d\u0129</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 nh\u1edd chi\u1ec1u cao l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1edfi \u00f4ng Park kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c V\u0103n H\u1eadu ph\u1ea3i \u2018\u1edf nh\u00e0\u2019\u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh hai \u0111\u00e0n anh B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Bahrain c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn t\u1ed1t, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i nh\u1eb1m ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i c\u00e1c pha treo b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o trong c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua, sau khi \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Park \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c\u00a0b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea1i cho Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u00f2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL s\u1ebd di chuy\u1ec3n sang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1m v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed V\u0103n H\u1eadu. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Bahrain ch\u01a1i thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/3-doi-hinh-co-the-duoc-thay-Park-su-dung-o-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi trung v\u1ec7 Th\u00e0nh Chung d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, l\u00fac n\u00e0y trong tay HLV Park Hang Seo ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb l\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho V\u0103n L\u1ee3i. N\u1ebfu \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e9t v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng khi anh \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 12 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017, L\u1ee3i \"Puyol\" \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang-seo ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 khi \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, L\u1ee3i \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn anh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 l\u00f2ng tin c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u1ee3i l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd n\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 l\u00ec \u0111\u00f2n h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn V\u0103n L\u1ee3i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110TQG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/lineup-(1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<h2>3. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-1-4-1. Khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 V\u0103n Thanh, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao l\u1ea1i cho \u0110\u1ee9c Huy. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n t\u1eeb xa nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Bahrain.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Bahrain, v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e2ng l\u00ean qu\u00e1 cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng hai bi\u00ean. N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1edf s\u01b0\u1eddn, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha leo bi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/lineup-(2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/link-sopcast/xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-302-195163.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/link-sopcast/xem-truc-tiep-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-bahrain-asiad-2018-302-195163.html\">Link xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nLink xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Bahrain tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truoc-tran-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-bahrain-cho-doi-luong-xuan-truong-168-195148.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain: T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng th\u00f4i L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng!</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ec3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/4-cau-hoi-dat-ra-cho-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-viet-nam-vs-bahrain-168-195141.html\">4 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain</span><br>\r\nV\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2694","checkdouble":"195162"},{"date":"16:12 23/08","title":"Real Madrid chi 36 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/real-madrid-chi-36-trieu-bang-mua-iago-aspas.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng, khi M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. Trong \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean tham gia chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1 tr\u1eadn. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Brighton b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tottenham, 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh &ndash; Antonio Valencia v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Mirror, c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y nu\u1ed1t tr\u1ecdng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng xung tr\u1eadn n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c\" title=\"M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/matic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Valencia d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8. Matic, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ngh\u1ec9 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Man United c\u0169ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot. C\u1ea3 2 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V b\u1eb1ng d\u00f2ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1edbm t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Tottenham Hotspur, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fan-mu-thue-chuyen-co-giang-bieu-ngu-sa-thai-ed-woodward-172-195133.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/2/12/ceo-cua-mu-nhuc-dau-vi-thanh-tich-cua-leicester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fan-mu-thue-chuyen-co-giang-bieu-ngu-sa-thai-ed-woodward-172-195133.html\">Fan M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 gi\u0103ng bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward</span><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward, v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3-172-195132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3-172-195132.html\">V\u00ec sao M.U b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3?</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho t\u1eeb ph\u00eda M.U gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e9m, sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2693","checkdouble":"195164"},{"date":"16:10 23/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Chelsea gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch NHA","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/ashley-cole-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ashley Cole ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng CLB c\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi tay t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2018/19. Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield Town, The Blues ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal 3-2 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng lo l\u1eafng d\u00e0nh cho Chelsea sau khi sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 m\u1eddi Sarri l\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi tri\u1ebft l\u00fd m\u1edbi nhanh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ashley Cole ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ashley Cole ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea m\u00f9a 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/ashley-cole-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u NHA</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ashley Cole tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAshley Cole t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Chelsea gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2009/10. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng CLB c\u0169 n\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c l\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5 Man City trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ngay c\u1ea3 khi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cChelsea c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat y\u00ean \u1eafng tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi\u201d, Ashley Cole ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean ESPN FC. \u201cH\u1ecd n\u00ean chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho danh hi\u1ec7u d\u00f9 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAshley Cole t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f9ng Arsenal trong 2 m\u00f9a 2001/02 v\u00e0 2003/04. Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 n\u01a1i HLV Unai Emery nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, anh t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan: <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi Arsenal, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi song t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f3 r\u1ea5t cao (thua 2 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea). T\u1eeb gi\u1edd tr\u1edf \u0111i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay-172-195111.html\">Ashley Cole \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u0103m nay</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ngolo-kante-toan-dien-nhu-the-nao-duoi-thoi-hlv-sarri-172-195088.html\">NGolo Kante to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-dai-dien-tang-boc-jorginho-sau-khoi-dau-trong-mo-o-chelsea-172-195082.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c Jorginho sau kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u01a1 \u1edf Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-2-doi-bong-thanh-madrid-vu-marcos-alonso-172-195078.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid v\u1ee5 Marcos Alonso</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lucas-piazon-sap-roi-chelsea-172-195071.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sang Ligue 1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2692","checkdouble":"195165"},{"date":"16:14 23/08","title":"HLV Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar m\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng B\u1ea1c World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/hlv-brazil-khang-dinh-neymar-moi-xung-dang-qua-bong-bac-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tite qua \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u00f4i sao ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n k\u1ecbch k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Brazil m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 thua B\u1ec9. Theo m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd t\u1ea5t y\u1ebfu m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, Neymar v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ch\u1ecbu s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite c\u1ee7a Brazil b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Tite c\u1ee7a Brazil b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/neymar-co-vai-loi-muon-nhan-gui-fan-ham-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Tite c\u1ee7a Brazil b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf PSG v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 k\u1ec7ch c\u1ee1m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u00ec b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tite v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi thanh minh cho l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng k\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 57 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 Neymar: \u201cNeymar ch\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, t\u1eeb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng x\u1eed hay s\u1ef1 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 thao. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi, anh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00ecnh kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u01b0 qu\u00fd v\u1ecb c\u1ea3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, Neymar ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ngay ch\u00ednh trong k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 Luka Modric r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec th\u00ec sao? Eden Hazard, kh\u00f4ng. Mohamed Salah, xin l\u1ed7i. \u0110\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, Thibaut Courtois c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111o\u1ea1t G\u0103ng Tay V\u00e0ng sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cau-chuyen-ve-neymar-cuoc-chien-khong-hoi-ket-giua-barca-va-real-madrid-184-192484.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/cau-chuyen-ve-neymar-cuoc-chien-khong-hoi-ket-giua-barca-va-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/cau-chuyen-ve-neymar-cuoc-chien-khong-hoi-ket-giua-barca-va-real-madrid-184-192484.html\">C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Neymar: Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Barca v\u00e0 Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nBarcelona t\u1eebng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Neymar. Nh\u01b0ng ti\u1ec3u Pele c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia v\u1ec1 n\u1ed7i \u0111au Luis Figo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2691","checkdouble":"195167"},{"date":"17:02 23/08","title":"M.U \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Spurs","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mu-don-hang-loat-tru-cot-tro-lai-truoc-tran-gap-spurs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0103n m\u1eebng, khi M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tour du \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. Trong \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean tham gia chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1 tr\u1eadn. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn trong vi\u1ec7c s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Brighton b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tottenham, 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh &ndash; Antonio Valencia v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Mirror, c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y nu\u1ed1t tr\u1ecdng b\u00e0i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng xung tr\u1eadn n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Mourinho l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c\" title=\"M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/matic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Matic v\u00e0 Valencia \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, Valencia d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8. Matic, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ngh\u1ec9 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Man United c\u0169ng ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot. C\u1ea3 2 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V b\u1eb1ng d\u00f2ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1edbm t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai t\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Tottenham Hotspur, b\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c M.U \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fan-mu-thue-chuyen-co-giang-bieu-ngu-sa-thai-ed-woodward-172-195133.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/2/12/ceo-cua-mu-nhuc-dau-vi-thanh-tich-cua-leicester.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fan-mu-thue-chuyen-co-giang-bieu-ngu-sa-thai-ed-woodward-172-195133.html\">Fan M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 gi\u0103ng bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward</span><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward, v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3-172-195132.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3-172-195132.html\">V\u00ec sao M.U b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3?</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho t\u1eeb ph\u00eda M.U gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e9m, sau nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2690","checkdouble":"195168"},{"date":"17:24 23/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00ea Wenger kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Emery","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/them-mot-cau-thu-che-wenger-khong-bang-emery.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 tr\u1ea3i qua 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nIwobi b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c Emery<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 22 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, &ldquo;Gi\u00e1o s\u01b0&rdquo; Wenger \u0111\u00e3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia Unai Emery \u0111\u1ebfn thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u1ea3 quan. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, 2 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf Premier League khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u1ea1i xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, sao tr\u1ebb Iwobi cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111em l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch cho t\u00f4i (so v\u1edbi th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Wenger). \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y s\u1eafc b\u00e9n h\u01a1n, gi\u1eef phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111ang th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn h\u01a1n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp\" title=\"Iwobi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/them-mot-cau-thu-che-wenger-khong-bang-emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery sau 2 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao, v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y (Emery), t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Emery, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u00f3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho Arsenal, b\u1edfi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i di\u1ec5n ra, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, d\u00f9 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo; &ndash; Alex Iwobi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 HLV Emery.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-khich-le-leno-khi-mat-vi-tri-ve-tay-cech-172-195125.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/sao-arsenal-khich-le-leno-khi-mat-vi-tri-ve-tay-cech.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-khich-le-leno-khi-mat-vi-tri-ve-tay-cech-172-195125.html\">Sao Arsenal kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 Leno khi m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1ec1 tay Cech</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Shkodran Mustafi l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khi t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Unai Emery tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf Emirates.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay-172-195111.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ashley-cole-danh-gia-trai-nguoc-arsenal-va-chelsea-nam-nay-172-195111.html\">Ashley Cole \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u0103m nay</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2689","checkdouble":"195169"},{"date":"17:30 23/08","title":"G\u00f3c Liverpool: Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/goc-liverpool-thai-tu-soan-ngoi-nha-vua-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu hy v\u1ecdng nh\u00e0 vua Manchester City b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi ngai v\u00e0ng trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ni\u1ec1m tin ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Liverpool s\u1eafm vai th\u00e1i t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sau \u0111\u00e2y 9 th\u00e1ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian cho ph\u00e9p c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mua b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 tinh gi\u1ea3m \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, tri\u1ec3n khai n\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh g\u1ecdn v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n trong khi s\u1ed1 kh\u00e1c ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u00f3a m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, theo \u0111u\u1ed5i duy nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup. H\u1ecd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n sau World Cup, \u00e2m th\u1ea7m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u1eb7ng nh\u00ecn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 mua s\u1eafm trong ho\u1ea3ng lo\u1ea1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 201819 Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i vua ManCity h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 201819 Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i vua ManCity h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Liverpool-o-Premier-League-201819-Thai-tu-soan-ngoi-vua-ManCity-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Crystal Palace ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau The Kop, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t Selhurst Park ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau ng\u00f3t ngh\u00e9t ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 h\u01a1n b\u1ed1n n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea5t kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u01a1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1eabn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, ph\u1ea7n nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n m\u1ea5t ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ec1 tay Man City m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1t ra l\u00e0m sao. Burnley, Everton, Newcastle, Watford hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Swansea v\u00e0 West Brom \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u00f3 lu\u00f4n sa l\u1ea7y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-nghich-ly-cua-liverpool-logic-cua-chien-thang-172-195138.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/goc-nhin-nghich-ly-cua-liverpool-logic-cua-chien-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/goc-nhin-nghich-ly-cua-liverpool-logic-cua-chien-thang-172-195138.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nLiverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jurgen Klopp, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i ch\u00ednh n\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/alisson-becker-giai-ma-tan-binh-liverpool-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-172-191660.html\" target=\"_blank\">Alisson Becker</span> ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, v\u1edbi phong th\u00e1i t\u1ef1 tin Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ed1ng v\u1eafng trong khung g\u1ed7 t\u1eeb bao l\u00e2u nay, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u00f3a b\u1eb1ng hai pha tr\u1ed5 t\u00e0i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u1eeb tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng trong ch\u00e2n. M\u1ea5t 8 tr\u1eadn n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi v\u00e0 gi\u1edd, s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t qu\u00e1 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n kh\u00e1c b\u1eaft hay h\u01a1n v\u00e0 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d</em> \u2013 Gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac nh\u01b0 Jurgen Klopp c\u00f2n c\u1ee5t l\u1ee7n v\u00e0 l\u1ea1nh l\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Loris Karius c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00f4ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn h\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c Liverpool Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c Liverpool Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Goc-Liverpool-Thai-tu-soan-ngoi-nha-vua-Man-City-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh Naby Keita</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Naby Keita m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t s\u00e2u s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. N\u1ed7i kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ng sinh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ea5y \u1edf Anfield \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n \u1edf ph\u00fat 22 khi Liverpool tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 sau m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace. Keita quay l\u01b0ng v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb Alisson, v\u1edbi c\u00fa gi\u1eadt g\u00f3t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf Townsend lao l\u00ean t\u1eeb \u0111\u1eb1ng sau, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 d\u0169ng m\u00e3nh v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 v\u00e0 b\u1ea5m b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn cho Salah \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Hennessey.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00fat \u0111i m\u1ecdi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c pressing \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi g\u00e2y l\u00ean c\u1ea3 h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, r\u00ea d\u1eaft v\u00e0i nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i t\u1ef1 th\u00e2n ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m cho Liverpool. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn trong v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 5 gi\u00e2y, c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 ai \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi bi\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e3 h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho-172-194447.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u): Vua \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-cuoi-giac-mo-cua-deco-de-nhi-172-194449.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i): Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a Deco \u0111\u1ec7 nh\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, Keita kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o khi ch\u1ec9 \u00edt l\u00e2u sau, anh ch\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Townsend nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 an \u1ee7i b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp khi chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng sai \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 ngay ngo\u00e0i r\u00eca c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a x\u00e0 ngang khung th\u00e0nh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eb3ng quan tr\u1ecdng, nh\u1eefng Kopites kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1ec1 h\u00e0 x\u00ed x\u00f3a cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ed5n nh\u1ea5t hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1o ra cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ea7u n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, Keita mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t, l\u00e0 c\u1ed9i ngu\u1ed3n \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi ng\u00f3c ng\u00e1ch tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng pitch. B\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c, \u0111\u00f4i ba nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-duoc-khen-hay-hon-ca-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-172-194443.html\" target=\"_blank\">phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a N\u2019Golo Kante</span> d\u1ea7n d\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u00e0 \u00edt n\u1ef1c c\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool\" title=\"Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19: Th\u00e1i t\u1eed so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 vua Man City?</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh Selhurst Park c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Crystal Palace v\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n tay d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Roy Hodgson, m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 xuy\u00ean ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Aaron Wan-Bissaka v\u00e0 Patrick Van Aanholt \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Premier League, trong khi Mamadou Sakho v\u00e0 James Tomkins t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady \u00e1n ng\u1eef tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00eam h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jurgen Klopp, b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0o qua 15 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t b\u00ean nhau, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu b\u00e0n thua m\u1ed7i 158 ph\u00fat. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn hai l\u1ea7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng trong 90 ph\u00fat.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 Liverpool m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu hy v\u1ecdng nh\u00e0 vua Manchester City b\u1ecb h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 kh\u1ecfi ngai v\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 Liverpool m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eafm vai th\u00e1i t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng so\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sau \u0111\u00e2y 9 th\u00e1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&autoplay=false&urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h2><strong>Liverpool \u1edf Premier League 2018/19:<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang-172-193863.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-liverpool-truoc-them-nha-201819-da-den-luc-nghi-ve-ngai-vang-172-193863.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Premier League 2018/19: \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 ngai v\u00e0ng</span><br>\r\n28 n\u0103m, g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u00f4i qua, c\u00e1c C\u0110V trung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u1eabn m\u1ecfi m\u00f2n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2688","checkdouble":"195171"},{"date":"17:54 23/08","title":"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/3-ly-do-khien-arsenal-khoi-dau-mua-giai-te-hai-duoi-thoi-emery.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Emery v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e1t nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh.</h2><h2>Thi\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/22/3-ly-do-khien-Arsenal-khoi-dau-te-hai-duoi-thoi-Emery-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Arsenal \u0111ang r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. V\u1edbi qu\u1ef9 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 n\u1ed5i nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Ousmane Dembele hay Wilfried Zaha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ozil, Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Iwobi trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Arsenal. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i Iwobi, hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 10. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng v\u00ec thi\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 minh ch\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u00e0n thua quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00e0 Arsenal ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea.</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Arsenal\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Emery ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c cho Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 qua, Arsenal \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere v\u00e0 Santi Cazorla. Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 h\u1ed3i h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey, Granit Xhaka v\u00e0 Mohamed Elneny.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nEmery \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trong 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Xhaka v\u00e0 Guendouzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn. Ramsey th\u00ec b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 y\u1ebfu \u1edbt khi\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi 1/3 s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, n\u01a1i m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng Aubameyang, Lacazette v\u00e0 Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u00e0o trong hi\u1ec7p hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Chelsea. Xhaka c\u0169ng b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eeb khi HLV Emery t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng th\u00ec Arsenal v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea3nh th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng d\u00e0i d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal\" title=\"Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/175050-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Arsenal ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i Guendouzi, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1ea1o n\u00ean nh\u1eefng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u1eeb Cech \u0111\u1ebfn Aubameyang, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eabn lung lay, h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng Arsenal l\u1ea1i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c phung ph\u00ed nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. D\u1ec5 th\u1ea5y t\u1ea1i sao Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Arsenal l\u00fac n\u00e0y qu\u00e1 r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a HLV Emery. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ed5i l\u1eeda v\u00e0o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-bi-canh-bao-mat-cho-ve-tay-tan-binh-172-195156.html\">Sao Arsenal b\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o m\u1ea5t ch\u1ed7 v\u1ec1 tay t\u00e2n binh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-khich-le-leno-khi-mat-vi-tri-ve-tay-cech-172-195125.html\">Sao Arsenal kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 Leno khi m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1ec1 tay Cech</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2687","checkdouble":"195172"},{"date":"17:56 23/08","title":"Benjamin Mendy: S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/23/benjamin-mendy-su-tro-lai-manh-me-cua-mot-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Benjamin Mendy t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Benjamin Mendy \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Arsenal v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch v\u00e0 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Huddersfield 6-1 t\u1ea1i Etihad. V\u1edbi 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng (+7), th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Pep Guardiola \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y&nbsp;m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benjamin Mendy t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Benjamin Mendy t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Benjamin-Mendy-toa-sang-ruc-ro-Su-tro-lai-cua-mot-bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City to\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Benjamin Mendy l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111ang t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield, Mendy l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7, \u1edf kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng anh c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ef1u sao Monaco l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n gi\u00fap Sergio Aguero ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00fa hat-trick.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, Mendy th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 12 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Man City, anh ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 112 l\u1ea7n (ch\u1ec9 sau John Stones, 116), th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 74 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 91%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal c\u1ef1u sao Monaco c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva ghi b\u00e0n. Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n 3 l\u1ea7n ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City dang dat phong do cuc cao\" title=\"Man City \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/mendy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Mendy l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Man City (196 l\u1ea7n), ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 16 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, g\u1ea5p h\u01a1n 5 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi David Silva (3), ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ebfp sau.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Fabian Delph, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Mendy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMendy c\u00f3 trung b\u00ecnh 8 l\u1ea7n qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng/90 ph\u00fat \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 0.67 l\u1ea7n/90 ph\u00fat c\u1ee7a Delph. S\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng/90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pep v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Mendy l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 6 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ebfn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Man City. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Pep Guardiola v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mendy to ra rat toan dien\" title=\"Mendy t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/mendy-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mendy t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00f4 t\u1eadn, Mendy c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 trong 90 ph\u00fat m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1eabn b\u00f3ng l\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Mendy, Man City c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 sang t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng. C\u1ef1u sao Monaco to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n h\u01a1n Fabian Delph r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Delph ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, nh\u01b0ng g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 Leroy Sane g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Man City.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Mendy \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Man City. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal, anh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu cho Raheem Sterling. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Huddersfield, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban do nhiet cua Mendy trong tran thang Huddersfield\" title=\"B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Mendy trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/mendy-3.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Mendy trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Huddersfield</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMendy \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 7 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19, 3 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Mendy gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn t\u1eeb HLV Pep Guardiola: &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam cho Man City ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i tin Mendy c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c, Mendy t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau khi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Man City, anh mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 Pep x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Mendy \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0 anh thu v\u1ec1 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2686","checkdouble":"195173"},{"date":"10:53 23/08","title":"\"Eden Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/28/eden-hazard-den-real-madrid-chi-la-chuyen-som-hay-muon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bermabeu ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard kh\u00f3 t\u1edbi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chuan-bi-gui-loi-de-nghi-cuoi-cung-vu-eden-hazard-180-195067.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real s\u1eafp g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i cho Hazard</span>, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u1eb1m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Chelsea b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mbappe \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (sau Neymar, 222 tri\u1ec7u euro).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Danny-Murphy-phat-bieu-ve-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hazard mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Khi m\u00e0 phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, n\u1ebfu Chelsea b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i h\u1ecd s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 c\u0169ng cam k\u1ebft s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Hazard chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, c\u00f2n chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ngay b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Danny Murphy tin Hazard ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool v\u00e0 Tottenham kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bermabeu ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1edbm hay mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Danny Murphy ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Danny Murphy tin Hazard t\u1edbi Real ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Real Madrid, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bernabeu, nh\u01b0ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i, Hazard \u0111ang r\u1ea5t chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c l\u00f2ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i cho Real. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i tin Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2019\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Hazard \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n t\u1eeb Chelsea, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u1ec9 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi The Blues hay kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2685","checkdouble":"195130"},{"date":"11:01 23/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Liverpool ch\u01b0a nh\u1ea3 Origi cho Dortmund","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/23/liverpool-muon-dortmund-mua-dut-divock-origi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi d\u00f9 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c hay sau 1 n\u0103m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd l\u1eddi h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Origi b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDivock Origi gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool t\u1eeb Lille v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2014. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng song ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 hi\u1ebfm khi ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2016/17 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Origi t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 43 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi \u0111a s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/liverpool-muon-dortmund-mua-dut-divock-origi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah r\u1ed3i c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Sadio Mane v\u00e0 Roberto Firmino, Origi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Wolfsburg song c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 6 b\u00e0n sau 34 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng. Ngo\u00e0i b\u1ed9 ba Mane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Daniel Sturridge, Adam Lallana, Xherdan Shaqiri ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Rhian Brewster, Dominic Solanke hay Sheyi Ojo\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool-172-194245.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/7/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/them-mot-tien-dao-sap-chia-tay-liverpool-172-194245.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafp chia tay Liverpool</span><br>\r\n<span>Fenerbahce mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Divock Origi r\u1eddi Liverpool, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua \u0111\u1ee9t hay kh\u00f4ng.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool m\u1edf c\u1eeda cho Origi ra \u0111i v\u00e0 ra gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Dortmund. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh trong v\u00f2ng 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n mua \u0111\u1ee9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Liverpool mu\u1ed1n Dortmund mua \u0111\u1ee9t Divock Origi ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ho\u1eb7c b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m. Khi m\u00e0 Origi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n giao k\u00e8o v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh, Liverpool quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef quan \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Dortmund \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool xu\u1ed1ng thang. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, The Kop d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e1n Danny Ings v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 24 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y song r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 anh t\u1edbi Southampton d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tham-hoa-thu-mon-chia-tay-liverpool-vao-cuoi-tuan-nay-172-194937.html\">Th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n chia tay Liverpool v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-194914.html\">Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chinh-thuc-thanh-ly-hang-ton-klavan-172-194741.html\">Liverpool CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C thanh l\u00fd h\u00e0ng t\u1ed3n Klavan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-cai-ten-tiep-theo-roi-liverpool-o-he-2018-172-194419.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! C\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi Liverpool \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2684","checkdouble":"195131"},{"date":"11:03 23/08","title":"V\u00ec sao M.U b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/vi-sao-mu-be-tac-y-tuong-tan-cong-o-mua-giai-thu-3.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mang \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Jurgen Klopp, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh</em> cho \u0111\u1ecbnh ngh\u0129a v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1eb7t ra. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n. 3 n\u0103m qua, Liverpool s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ee9 v\u0169 kh\u00ed s\u00e1t th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t song ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfc khi\u00ean th\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng mong manh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac m\u00e0 <em>ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Liverpool c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t</em> sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m. Th\u1eadt v\u1eady, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tottenham t\u1ea1i Wembley v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 2017 t\u1edbi nay, The Kop l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Liverpool-thang-2-tran-EPL.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a Liverpool. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u201cr\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ef1ng b\u00f3ng\u201d nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec3u, song nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 mong manh nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u00f3m \u201cBig Six\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi Liverpool, Klopp mang theo <strong>l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf, m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n song l\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro</strong>. Nh\u00ecn c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf thi \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1edb l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 50 th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, toan t\u00ednh trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf nhoi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Liverpool, logic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Goc-nhin-Nghich-ly-cua-Liverpool,-logic-cua-chien-thang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">T\u1eebng c\u00f3 l\u00fac The Kop \u0111\u1ea7y mong manh trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, <em>Liverpool s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i</em> v\u00e0 b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u00fac, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Klopp l\u00e0: \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ghi 3 b\u00e0n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ghi 4. H\u1ecd nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn binh c\u00f3 v\u0169 kh\u00ed kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp nh\u1ea5t, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf gi\u00e1p ra \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u0103ng hoa, Liverpool qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi li\u1ec1n t\u00f9 t\u00ec m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a ch\u1ec9nh xong trang ph\u1ee5c. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, The Kop c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1edbp nho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta t\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<u>Liverpool m\u00f9a 2018/19 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e1c</u>. H\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t h\u1ea1 West Ham 4-0 v\u00e0 Crystal Palace 2-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 l\u1ea7n sau 2 tr\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00ean khung th\u00e0nh Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hang thu Liverpool chac chan hon\" title=\"hang thu Liverpool chac chan hon\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/hang-thu-Liverpool-chac-chan-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng Liverpool hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nLogic c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ea7n l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1eafm l\u1ec7ch l\u1ea1c, thi\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn trong khi m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 (\u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c), b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League r\u1ed3i \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt l\u00ean y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd, ch\u1ec9 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng m\u1ea1nh c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. C\u1ea3 Real v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-sap-co-alisson-khi-bien-chat-tao-nen-su-vi-dai-172-191590.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson: Khi \u201cbi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t\u201d t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Alisson sau khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 66 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho AS Roma. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp theo \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Klopp \u0111ang d\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi th\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c</strong> \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool. Trong tay \u00f4ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u00ecn t\u00ean c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n thua ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, <u>Liverpool c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n</u>. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 mang t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u l\u1ea1c quan. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t anh, Virgil van Dijk ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng ngay ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd tho\u00e1t pressing h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" title=\"Alisson cua Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/23/Alisson-cua-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Alisson g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n \"l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c\" Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Van Dijk, Joe Gomez ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 2 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham v\u00e0 Crystal Palace, \u0111\u00e1nh tan ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nghi ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1 thay Dejan Lovren. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p nguy kh\u00f3, c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Naby Keita c\u00e0y \u1ea3i nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 <em>nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Liverpool</em>. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng thay v\u00ec g\u1eddn g\u1ee3n c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ng\u00e0y vui s\u1edbm t\u00e0n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. C\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi Liverpool ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Klopp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t Liverpool c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m, th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u \u0111ang d\u1ea7n bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn cho C\u0110V c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Liverpool \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League sau 28 n\u0103m ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i. Th\u1ee9 7 n\u00e0y, v\u00f2ng 3 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho Brighton tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield?<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):</strong>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&autoplay=false&urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-ve-naby-keita-phan-1-vua-cua-duong-pho-172-194447.html\">Chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 Naby Keita (Ph\u1ea7n 1): Vua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-40-west-ham-khi-chiec-ao-khong-lam-nen-thay-tu-172-194355.html\">Liverpool 4-0 West Ham: Khi chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean th\u1ea7y tu</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-dau-palace-02-liverpool-172-195001.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-ly-do-tin-tuong-liverpool-se-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-172-195092.html\">Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Liverpool s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2683","checkdouble":"195132"},{"date":"10:53 23/08","title":"Fan M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 gi\u0103ng bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/2/12/ceo-cua-mu-nhuc-dau-vi-thanh-tich-cua-leicester.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward, v\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nFan M.U kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y ra h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. Man United m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 thua thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester City \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1. Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng gi\u1eefa PCT Ed Woodward v\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Jose Mourinho c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00ednh h\u00ecnh tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111em v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh, trong khi Ed Woodward l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0y hay ho cho l\u1eafm. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho li\u00ean h\u1ec7 trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0o c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward\" title=\"Ed Woodward \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Man Utd\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/2/12/ceo-cua-mu-nhuc-dau-vi-thanh-tich-cua-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Turf Moor c\u1ee7a Burnley t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Man United \u0111ang l\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ecb PCT ki\u00eam G\u0110\u0110H n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef <strong>&ldquo;ED OUT &ndash; LUHT&rdquo;</strong> \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n, v\u1edbi \u00fd ngh\u0129a: <em>&ldquo;Ed Woodward c\u1ea7n ra \u0111i, Y\u00eau M.U nh\u01b0ng gh\u00e9t nh\u00e0 Glazer (Love United Hate Glazer).</em><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Man United, khi chi\u1ebfc chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 bay ngang SV\u0110 c\u00f9ng d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef &ldquo;Wrong One &ndash; Moyes Out&rdquo;. V\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t C\u0110V M.U thu\u00ea chuy\u00ean c\u01a1 \u0111\u00f2i sa th\u1ea3i Ed Woodward &ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man United, h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9, b\u00e0i to\u00e1n m\u00e0 Jose Mourinho c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-man-united-con-khong-bang-roma-172-195119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/12/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-man-united-con-khong-bang-roma.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-danh-gia-man-united-con-khong-bang-roma-172-195119.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Man United c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Roma</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Patrick Kluivert l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U, ch\u1ecdn AS Roma l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi cho c\u1eadu con trai.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dang-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-su-sup-do-cua-hang-thu-172-195058.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/dang-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-su-sup-do-cua-hang-thu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dang-sau-tran-thua-soc-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-su-sup-do-cua-hang-thu-172-195058.html\">\u0110\u1eb1ng sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton: S\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nghi ng\u1edd t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y M.U ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2682","checkdouble":"195133"},{"date":"11:20 23/08","title":"Chelsea \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Willian cho Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/11/chelsea-doi-y-bat-ngo-muon-ban-willian-cho-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid mua Willian l\u1ea1i m\u1edf ra, theo Mirror Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Willian b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Braizl l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. M.U v\u00e0 Barca quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea m\u1edf c\u1eeda gi\u00fap Real Madrid mua Willian  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea m\u1edf c\u1eeda gi\u00fap Real Madrid mua Willian  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/23/Chelsea-mo-cua-giup-Real-Madrid-mua-Willian--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988, song Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford. Sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 50, 53 v\u00e0 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Willian bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Malcom.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-muon-chi-100-trieu-bang-cho-courtois-va-willian-180-192290.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Willian</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Chelsea v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn, HLV Sarri tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Willian \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Real Madrid mua Willian l\u1ea1i m\u1edf ra, theo Mirror Chelsea b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" title=\"Willian ghi ban cho Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Willian-noi-ve-viec-chuyen-den-MU-o-ky-chuyen-nhuong-He-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh ra b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Pedro, Morata v\u00e0 Hazard.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPedro \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua anh \u0111\u1ec1u ghi b\u00e0n, gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield v\u00e0 Arsenal. HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pedro, \u00f4ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, Chelsea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Willian b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n anh cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. HLV Lopetegui v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, n\u1ebfu Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Willian l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2681","checkdouble":"195136"}]}